videos.description: Immanuel Quickley and Nick Richards exchange powerful dunks for Kentucky in the first half vs. Texas Tech.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Quickley, Richards wreck the rim for Kentucky) 2020/1/25

videos.headline: Quickley, Richards wreck the rim for Kentucky

videos.description: Kentucky guard Immanuel Quickley's prayer from half court falls to beat the first-half buzzer.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Quickley drills half-court heave at the horn) 2020/1/25

videos.headline: Quickley drills half-court heave at the horn

videos.description: Immanuel Quickley and Davide Moretti both miss 3-pointers for Kentucky and Texas Tech, respectively, as the game is sent to overtime.

videos.headline: Kentucky, Texas Tech miss game-winning attempts

videos.description: Texas Tech's Davide Moretti loses the ball out of bounds, and after review, it is ruled Kentucky ball to give the Wildcats a road victory.
